First Department,

March, 1949.

(March 3, 1949.) 308 West 82nd Street Corporation et al., Appellants, v. Sumray, Inc., et al., Respondents, et al., Defendants.

Present — Peck, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Yan Yoorhis, JJ.; Peck, P. J., dissents and votes to affirm. [See post, p. 709.]
